Noi decidem daca murim sau nu.

522
01:11:38.612 --> 01:11:44.522
Suntem barbaai ai uniai...

523
01:11:44.523 --> 01:11:46.325
Vreai sa traiai?

524
01:11:46.326 --> 01:11:48.830
